data.name: labelDomeShutterStatus.ToolTip
data.value:
Shutter status The shutter status can be one of the following: - open: Doors are within 5cm from maximal range - closed: Doors are within 5cm of minimal range - opening: The motors are actively opening the doors - closing: The motors are actively closing the doors - error: The last reading of the distance between the doors (via WiFi) resulted in an error
If the distance between the doors is available (read via WiFi), the calculated opening percent is shown in paranthesis.
